20#ifndef _ELF_BFIN_H
21#define _ELF_BFIN_H
22
23#include "elf/reloc-macros.h"
24
25START_RELOC_NUMBERS (elf_bfin_reloc_type)
26 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_UNUSED0, 0x00) /* relocation type 0 is not defined */
27 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_PCREL5M2, 0x01) /* LSETUP part a */
28 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_UNUSED1, 0x02) /* relocation type 2 is not defined */
29 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_PCREL10, 0x03) /* type 3, 0x00) if cc jump <target> */
30 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_PCREL12_JUMP, 0x04) /* type 4, 0x00) jump <target> */
31 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_RIMM16, 0x05) /* type 0x5, 0x00) rN = <target> */
32 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_LUIMM16, 0x06) /* # 0x6, 0x00) preg.l=<target> Load imm 16 to lower half */
33 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_HUIMM16, 0x07) /* # 0x7, 0x00) preg.h=<target> Load imm 16 to upper half */
34 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_PCREL12_JUMP_S, 0x08) /* # 0x8 jump.s <target> */
35 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_PCREL24_JUMP_X, 0x09) /* # 0x9 jump.x <target> */
36 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_PCREL24, 0x0a) /* # 0xa call <target> , 0x00) not expandable */
37 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_UNUSEDB, 0x0b) /* # 0xb not generated */
38 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_UNUSEDC, 0x0c) /* # 0xc not used */
39 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_PCREL24_JUMP_L, 0x0d) /* 0xd jump.l <target> */
40 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_PCREL24_CALL_X, 0x0e) /* 0xE, 0x00) call.x <target> if <target> is above 24 bit limit call through P1 */
41 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_VAR_EQ_SYMB, 0x0f) /* 0xf, 0x00) linker should treat it same as 0x12 */
42 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_BYTE_DATA, 0x10) /* 0x10, 0x00) .byte var = symbol */
43 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_BYTE2_DATA, 0x11) /* 0x11, 0x00) .byte2 var = symbol */
44 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_BYTE4_DATA, 0x12) /* 0x12, 0x00) .byte4 var = symbol and .var var=symbol */
45 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_PCREL11, 0x13) /* 0x13, 0x00) lsetup part b */
46 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_GOT17M4, 0x14)
47 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_GOTHI, 0x15)
48 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_GOTLO, 0x16)
49 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_FUNCDESC, 0x17)
50 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_FUNCDESC_GOT17M4, 0x18)
51 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_FUNCDESC_GOTHI, 0x19)
52 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_FUNCDESC_GOTLO, 0x1a)
53 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_FUNCDESC_VALUE, 0x1b)
54 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_FUNCDESC_GOTOFF17M4, 0x1c)
55 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_FUNCDESC_GOTOFFHI, 0x1d)
56 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_FUNCDESC_GOTOFFLO, 0x1e)
57 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_GOTOFF17M4, 0x1f)
58 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_GOTOFFHI, 0x20)
59 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_GOTOFFLO, 0x21)
60
61 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_PUSH, 0xE0)
62 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_CONST, 0xE1)
63 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_ADD, 0xE2)
64 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_SUB, 0xE3)
65 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_MULT, 0xE4)
66 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_DIV, 0xE5)
67 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_MOD, 0xE6)
68 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_LSHIFT, 0xE7)
69 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_RSHIFT, 0xE8)
70 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_AND, 0xE9)
71 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_OR, 0xEA)
72 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_XOR, 0xEB)
73 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_LAND, 0xEC)
74 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_LOR, 0xED)
75 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_LEN, 0xEE)
76 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_NEG, 0xEF)
77 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_COMP, 0xF0)
78 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_PAGE, 0xF1)
79 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_HWPAGE, 0xF2)
80 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_ADDR, 0xF3)
81 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_PLTPC, 0x40) /* PLT gnu only relocation */
82 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_GOT, 0x41) /* GOT gnu only relocation */
83 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_GNU_VTINHERIT, 0x42) /* C++, gnu only */
84 RELOC_NUMBER (R_BFIN_GNU_VTENTRY, 0x43) /* C++, gnu only */
85END_RELOC_NUMBERS (R_BFIN_max)
86
87/* Processor specific flags for the ELF header e_flags field. */
88#define EF_BFIN_PIC 0x00000001 /* -fpic */
89#define EF_BFIN_FDPIC 0x00000002 /* -mfdpic */
90
91#define EF_BFIN_CODE_IN_L1 0x00000010 /* --code-in-l1 */
92#define EF_BFIN_DATA_IN_L1 0x00000020 /* --data-in-l1 */
93
94#define EF_BFIN_PIC_FLAGS (EF_BFIN_PIC | EF_BFIN_FDPIC)
95#endif /* _ELF_BFIN_H */
